result.name: Eight Delicious Fresh Dumpling Rice

reviews.text: It is good for a simple and quick meal. Its dumplings are very nice with northeen style taste and flavour. I also tried egg plant, mapo toff, sour fish bowl and sour and sweet fried pork, all are better than average. Restaurant hall is small and tight. The owner and staffs are friendly as like neighbors in the town. Take out orders are available with tidy PP bowl packing.
really yummy local sichuan food i love the popcorn chicken and the sichuan fish! plus the menu is in english, beware they charge extra for napkins!
Basic and authentic Shanghai food.  Good taste with reasonable price
Dumplings just ok, good for quick bite. Waitress speak Mandarin.
nice value for money!
